<div class="content">
  <h1>Phlogs of the Moxie</h1>
  <p>Flickr was too new to use back in the heady days of early 2005, so I decided to take matters into my own hands and collect photos in these hand-spun picture posts. And in case you were wondering, photos + blog = phlog.</p>
</div>

<% @phlogs.each do |phlog| %>
  <div class="content-sidebar phlog-index">
    <div class="sidebar">
      <%= link_to image_tag("http://moxie.danchilton.com/pix/phlog/thumbs/#{phlog.thumbnail}"), make_phlog_link(phlog) %>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h3><%= link_to phlog.title, make_phlog_link(phlog) %></h3>
      <em><%= phlog.created_at.strftime("%b %-d, %Y @ %l:%M %P") %>, <%= pluralize(phlog.phlog_comments.size,"comment") %></em>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>